{"tid":41080,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"各位巴絲打，留低自己一生嘅遺憾","createTime":"2016-12-15T15:27:11.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-17T10:02:53.000Z","uid":66088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ef0466337d1e587390521bb3758c6a1067742dad","tid":41080,"uid":66088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T15:27:11.000Z","msg":"三十幾歲人，原來一個朋友都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n電話薄上面，沒有朋友嘅電話號碼出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11054513917db312eba73da4359351572e2ec88b","tid":41080,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T15:28:30.000Z","msg":"落左電話簿又點，咪又係唔會搵我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"737a2bffcd205c2a8e7d69e0b906b747ad2f341b","tid":41080,"uid":66088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T15:29:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>落左電話簿又點，咪又係唔會搵我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁超碼你自己可以主動搵人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我係連人都無得搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0538cac2d61afa31b2d815e165581f20755ef95","tid":41080,"uid":13317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T15:33:42.000Z","msg":"升中學嗰時無勇敢啲同老母講我真係好想升某間好勁好勁既中學 (當年運動好好實入到) 然後好遺憾覺得中學6年本應可以受到更好既教育 可以讀得更好<br />\n同埋可以繼續玩自己本來唔會放棄既運動<br />\n最後讀嗰間中學體育又差讀書又唔係特別出色<br />\n錯過左好多野<br />\n咁今日就唔洗讀乞食科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 更加唔會對我中學生活咁多遺憾"},{"pid":"0a867f7077aeb84b5f6a51a6615ee6b6186fbd2d","tid":41080,"uid":17832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T15:34:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bb5c23d797d1a42f2804f7a693c2f90edae79575","tid":41080,"uid":19560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T15:37:54.000Z","msg":"出生於呢個垃圾世界"},{"pid":"39edb6de5a71a66edc16496710a81aac118e9d31","tid":41080,"uid":60256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T15:39:25.000Z","msg":"曾經有一份真摯的愛情放係我面前，但係我冇好好咁珍惜"},{"pid":"07a101f6752d8f3643b56785b33ad396af773447","tid":41080,"uid":3303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T15:40:01.000Z","msg":"唔小心跌親 流左血"},{"pid":"4afa1aeeda98f8ec47cbe408a08eda8a17df53b1","tid":41080,"uid":66088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T15:42:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>升中學嗰時無勇敢啲同老母講我真係好想升某間好勁好勁既中學 (當年運動好好實入到) 然後好遺憾覺得中學6年本應可以受到更好既教育 可以讀得更好<br />\n同埋可以繼續玩自己本來唔會放棄既運動<br />\n最後讀嗰間中學體育又差讀書又唔係特別出色<br />\n錯過左好多野<br />\n咁今日就唔洗讀乞食科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 更加唔會對我中學生活咁多遺憾</blockquote><br />\n經過上次教訓，之後要勇敢啲表達自己喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a49a78db581a35466a79cf9036d64e925e1a3616","tid":41080,"uid":66088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T15:43:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>就係出錯世 原本應該係西德仔黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁我祝你你下世會係一個西人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ee1c93707a79b56edf7eeb5a87c9c25c12fc36b","tid":41080,"uid":3646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T15:44:30.000Z","msg":"做左香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d86127e257137388d7abe3cf987142381abd818e","tid":41080,"uid":66088,"like":0,"dis